channel.title: [CrackMe] CrackMe Simulator 2018
channel.description:
This is a PoC-style test run for an application that I am currently developing as a personal project. Should anything weird happen, please report it to me and I'll try to fix it. This is just a simple crackme so it shouldn't be too hard once you start to figure out what's happening... maybe...? :thinking:

#### Author Assigned Level: ¯\\\_(ツ)_/¯
#### Community Assigned Level: [poll type=regular] * Newbie * Wannabe * Hacker * Wizard * Guru [/poll]

## Objective
* Find the correct key.
---
## Rules of Engagement

---
